373
00:27:46,027 --> 00:27:48,727
夜は暖かくなるよ
The night will become warmer

374
00:27:49,027 --> 00:27:51,727
君はさ君のままで笑って
You, just smile while being yourself

375
00:27:52,027 --> 00:27:54,227
今日が
Today...

376
00:27:54,427 --> 00:27:57,027
今日がどうにも寂しくてさ
Today is just so lonely

377
00:27:57,427 --> 00:28:00,027
眠れないままだ夜だけどさ
I still can't sleep, though it's night

378
00:28:00,427 --> 00:28:03,027
いつか幸せって思えるまで
Until the day I can think I'm happy

379
00:28:03,427 --> 00:28:05,727
君は君のままでいてよ
Just keep being yourself

380
00:28:06,027 --> 00:28:08,727
もうさ強がらなくてもいいんだよ
It's okay, you don't have to act tough anymore

381
00:28:09,027 --> 00:28:11,727
過去の夜の涙ひとつ
Every single tear from nights in the past

382
00:28:12,027 --> 00:28:14,727
それを弱く持って歩いていく
I'll walk while holding them gently

383
00:28:15,027 --> 00:28:17,627
それだけで今はいいんだよ
Just that is okay for now

384
00:28:33,727 --> 00:28:36,727
制服のねねたち可愛かったよね！
The Nenes in uniforms were cute, weren't they!

385
00:28:37,227 --> 00:28:40,227
次はどの曲にしよう？
Which song should I choose next?

386
00:28:40,727 --> 00:28:44,227
ゲストは次で最後みたい。
It seems the next guests will be the last.

387
00:28:44,427 --> 00:28:47,727
その前に一回ねねのソロを挟んどく？
Before that, should I squeeze in a Nene solo?

388
00:28:48,327 --> 00:28:51,027
よし！この曲に決定！
Alright! I've decided on this song!

389
00:28:52,827 --> 00:28:56,527
次はアイドル曲だから、アイドルっぽい衣装で歌いたいな。
Since the next one is an idol song, I want to sing in an idol-like outfit.

390
00:28:57,327 --> 00:29:02,227
どの衣装にしようかな？
Which outfit should I choose?

391
