神様は将来の指輪を
God, please hide the ring

408
00:30:26,123 --> 00:30:28,323
どこかに隠してね
of the future somewhere

409
00:30:28,323 --> 00:30:33,623
君の好きに合わせた髪の色
The hair color matched to your preference

410
00:30:33,623 --> 00:30:36,923
私の中君だけで
Within me, there's only you

411
00:30:36,923 --> 00:30:39,923
満場一致は中毒へ
Unanimous agreement leads to addiction

412
00:30:39,923 --> 00:30:45,123
責任取ってね 大好きです
Take responsibility, I love you

413
00:30:45,123 --> 00:30:47,923
せーの！
One, two!

414
00:30:47,923 --> 00:30:53,923
絶対アイドル辞めないで
Never stop being an idol

415
00:30:53,923 --> 00:30:57,623
優しい目も真面目顔も
From your kind eyes to your serious face

416
