全幕 幕が開けた そのオノマトペ
The curtain rose on all acts with that onomatopoeia

472
00:35:22,068 --> 00:35:25,368
着飾る人形はピエロに口付けを
The dressed-up doll kisses the clown

473
00:35:25,468 --> 00:35:29,068
本日大団円 脚本が笑う
A grand finale today, the script is laughing

474
00:35:29,168 --> 00:35:32,468
騙されてくれる あなた達と
Together with you all who let me deceive you

475
00:35:32,568 --> 00:35:35,868
私今ここで何をしてる
What am I doing here right now?

476
00:35:50,168 --> 00:35:53,268
耳を劈く 拍手喝采
The ear-splitting applause

477
00:35:53,568 --> 00:35:56,668
ザルも踊ればヒトにもなれる
If even a monkey dances, it can become human

478
00:35:56,768 --> 00:35:59,968
フォーカスされた日常 引き金を描いて
A focused daily life, drawing the trigger

479
00:36:00,068 --> 00:36:03,168
演ずるように
As if performing

480
00:36:03,268 --> 00:36:06,468
一回 二回 三回 嘘を重ねて
Once, twice, thrice, piling up the lies

481
00:36:06,668 --> 00:36:10,968
十回 千回 億回 瞳を逸らして
Ten, a thousand, a hundred million times, averting my eyes

482
00:36:11,168 --> 00:36:14,468
誰なんだっけかな 私は あれ
Wait, who was I again? Oh...

483
00:36:17,468 --> 00:36:20,668
飽和した 仮面 ぶっ飛んで
The saturated mask flies off

484
00:36:20,768 --> 00:36:24,168
独りと孤独なワルツでお出迎え
Welcomed with a solo, lonely waltz

485
00:36:24,268 --> 00:36:27,668
脱作の中
Amidst the artifice

486
00:36:27,768 --> 00:36:29,168
あどけてみせて
Try to look innocent

487
00:36:29,268 --> 00:36:30,668
あどけてみせて
Try to look innocent

488
00:36:30,768 --> 00:36:37,168
あたしの世界はグルグル回ってく
My world keeps spinning round and round

489
00:36:38,168 --> 00:36:41,168
全幕 幕が開けた そのオノマトペ
The curtain rose on all acts with that onomatopoeia

490
00:36:41,368 --> 00:36:44,968
群がる人形はダリアの花束を
The swarming dolls hold bouquets of dahlias

491
00:36:45,068 --> 00:36:48,468
選んでくれた服を着て踊りましょう
Let's dance wearing the clothes you chose for me

492
00:36:48,568 --> 00:36:52,168
騙されてくれる あなた達と
Together with you all who let me deceive you

493
00:36:52,468 --> 00:36:57,168
いいよ もう これが好きだっただけなのだ
It's fine now, I just loved this, that's all

494
