本日大団円 脚本が笑う
A grand finale today, the script is laughing

505
00:38:09,368 --> 00:38:12,668
どうしようもないよな
There's nothing to be done, is there?

506
00:38:14,268 --> 00:38:18,668
どこを誰でもいい 調子に乗るなよと
Anyone, anywhere, just tell me not to get ahead of myself

507
00:38:18,768 --> 00:38:22,168
ただ言い聞かせてくれ
Just keep telling me that

508
00:38:22,268 --> 00:38:25,668
そういや夢も散々見てたな
Come to think of it, I've had plenty of dreams

509
00:38:25,768 --> 00:38:28,968
もう後戻りは叶わないと
Knowing there's no going back anymore

510
00:38:29,068 --> 00:38:31,668
気づけばそこには一人で
And I find myself there all alone

511
00:38:42,668 --> 00:38:46,168
振り落とせ ペルソナを
Shake off the persona

512
